    "Andrea Camerana is the nephew of iconic fashion designer Giorgio Armani (d. September 2025) and the son of his sister Rosanna Armani.",
    "He is a board member of Armani's namesake fashion firm and served as the company's managing director for sustainability.",
    "Under the terms of Armani's will, Andrea is entitled to 17% of the net proceeds from the sale or public listing of 45% of the company within five years of Armani's death.",
    "He also inherited some of Armani's shares in eyewear giant EssilorLuxottica as well as a stake in Armani's superyacht and his empire of luxury homes."
